imdb.plot outline: Here on What to Watch Before You Die, we're bringing you the full scoop on one great movie a week, letting you know what movies you need to see in your lifetime. If you think there's one (or more) movies that should be on our must-see list, follow Mackenzie on Instagram (@Mackwahl), and let her know what you'd like to see with using the hash tag #W2WBUD.
